{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/Main_CAP_2_616x353.png?t=1713494663\" /><br><br><i>Enter the world of Midnight of Despair, where every step is a test of your skill, patience, and determination. There are no shortcuts here \u2013 you'll need to finish in one go, no saving allowed. But fear not, because the journey is just as important as the destination, and every leap forward brings you closer to victory.</i><br><br><br><strong><strong>Gameplay</strong></strong><br><br>Simple yet challenging, Midnight of Despair is all about running, jumping, and timing your moves just right. Each section presents new obstacles and challenges that will push your skills to the limit.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/movemtresized.gif?t=1713494663\" /><br><br><br><strong>Dash mechanics</strong><br><br>When a regular jump won't cut it, it's time to dash. Master this mechanic to traverse gaps, evade hazards, and reach new heights. With practice, you'll become a master of the dash, soaring through map with precision and grace.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/DashResized.gif?t=1713494663\" /><br><br><strong>Checkpoints</strong><br><br>As you journey through the game, you'll encounter various characters in need of assistance. Help them out, and they'll reward you with valuable respawn points. These checkpoints are your lifeline, giving you a second chance when things get tough.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/GifNpc.gif?t=1713494663\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engaging dash mechanics add depth to the gameplay<br></li><li>High level of difficulty ensures a challenge for even the most seasoned pl